title: MU Volleyball wins thriller over (9) Florida
text:
MU Volleyball wins thriller over (9) Florida POSTED: 07:00 PM CDT Sep 30, 2015 UPDATED: 11:03 PM CDT Sep 30, 2015 
The Mizzou volleyball team defeats (9) Florida 3-2 after going down 2-0. Carly Kan had 17 kills and 13 digs. MU moves to 13-1 on the year.
